item.title: Third Bingo Request
item.content:encoded:
So I need another bingo (with note page, of course) for Anon. If anyone could do this for me, I would greatly appreciate it.

My stats: Lear/Level 51/The Wiki Village

Of course, I'm willing to bingo you in exchange. I've held back on getting Right specifically for that reason. Just leave your Village and name. Also, make sure your village isn't in peacetime (+4 or more) or too small to spy on easily. I have a pretty good range, but I can't hit everything.

Thanks in advance.
